"IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016302, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be on you O tested one tested by He who created you before He created you and you were patient on what He tested you with. We believe in you, and are your followers and we submit to all that was brought by your father, blessings of Allah be on him and his family and by his successor, peace be on him and we ask You, O Allah if we attest truly to them that You grant us an elevated status through it, so we can give ourselves good news that we have purified ourselves through their guardianship peace be on them.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "AS-SAALLAMO A'LAIY-KE YAA MUM-TAHANA-TUM TAHANA-KIL LAZEE KALAQA-KE QABLA AN YAKHLE-QAKE WA KUNTE LE-MAM TAHANA-KE BEHI SAABE-RATAN WA NAHNO LAKE AWLIYAAA-OON MOSADDE-QOONA, WA LE KULLE MAA ATAA BEHI ABOO-KE SALLAL-LAAHO A’LAIY-HE WA AALE-HI, WA ATAA BEHI WA SAIYYO-HU A’LAIY-HIS SALAAMO MOSALLE-MOONA WA NAHNO NAS-ALOKAL LAAHUMMA IZ KUNNA MOSADDE-QEENA LAHUM AN TUL-HEQANAA BE-TASDEE-QENAA BID-DARAJA-TIL A’ALE-YATE LENO-BASH-SHERA AN-FOSA-NAA BE-ANNAA QAD TAHUR-NAA BE-WELAAYATE-HIM A’LAIYHE-MUS SALAAM.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْکِ یَامُمْتَحَنَۃُ امْتَحَنَکِ الَّذِیْ خَلَقَکِ قَبْلَ اَنْ یَخْلِقَكِ وَكُنْتِ لِمَا امْتَحَنَكِ بِهٖ صَابِرَۃً وَنَحْنُ لَكِ اَوْلِیَاۗءٌ مُصَدِّقُوْنَ، وَلِكُلِّ مَا اَتٰی بِهٖ اَبُوْكِ صَلَّی اللهُ عَلَیْهِ وَآلِهٖ، وَاَتٰی بِهٖ وَصَیُّهٗ عَلَیْهِ السَّلَامُ مُسَلِّمُوْنَ وَنَحْنُ نَسْئَلُكَ اللّٰهُمَّ اِذْ كُنَّا مُصَدِّقِیْنَ لَهُمْ اَنْ تُلْحِقَنَا بِتَصْدِیْقِنَا بِالدَّرَجَۃِ الْعَالِیَۃِ لِنُبَشِّرَ اَنْفُسَنَا بِاَنَّا قَدْ طَهُرْنَا بِوِلَایَتِهِمْ عَلَیْهِمُ السَّلَامِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSig